text: This obsoletes IRM 25.23.6, Identity Protection and Victim Assistance, CSCO/ASFR IDT Processing

The material relating to the policy and guidance previously contained in IRM 25.23.6, Identity Protection and Victim Assistance, ACSS IDT Processing is incorporated into IRM 25.23.10, Protection and Victim Assistance, Compliance Identity Theft Case Processing.
Applies to all employees working in Identity Theft Victim Assistance (ITVA)-Compliance Programs.
